A birthday celebration is really for those who have lifted me up onto their bare shoulders to help me reach heights inconceivable alone. Though I will not share the photos of those individuals, I believe they know who they are; for the unspoken word is the most powerful. To those who know me as the quiet, critical, and sometimes lonely creature when all the glitz and glamour is over. To those who I confide in and laugh with in my weakest hours. I thank you all, and I hope you know that without you I would have no life force. Thank you for picking me up when im down, and pushing me onward when I have no strength. Without my loved ones and my fans, I am but a man with a dream. But with you, I am a man strong enough to chase this dream and live freely. I love you all. Thank you ♥️ #27
